**Exercise 1**.
```bash
cd ~
ls -l
```
**Exercise 2**.
```bash
du -ah /var/log | sort -h
```
**Exercise 3**.
```bash
nano firstname.txt
```
**Exercise 4**.
```bash
echo "Keskin" > lastname.txt
```
**Exercise 5**.
```bash
cat firstname.txt && lastname.txt
```
**Exercise 6**.
```bash
cat lastname.txt >> firstname.txt
```
**Exercise 7**.
```bash
ls -d ~/*/ > my_folders.txt
```


** Regular expressions hw (0-11)**
**Exercise 1**.
```bash
ls ~/ | grep -E '^[A-Z]'
```

**Exercise 2**.
```bash
ls -A ~/ | grep -E '^\.'
```

**Exercise 3**.
```bash
ls -A ~/ | grep -E '^\.' | wc -l
```

**Exercise 4**.
```bash
ls ~/ | grep -E '^[A-Za-z]+$'
```

**Exercise 5**.
```bash
ls ~/ | grep -E '^[^A-Z]+$'
```

**Exercise 6**.
```bash
ls ~/ | grep -E -v '\.[a-zA-Z]{3}$'
```

**Exercise 7**.
```bash
ls /etc | grep -E '^c.*y$'
```

**Exercise 8**.
```bash
ls /etc | grep -E 'ss'
```

**Exercise 9**.
```bash
ls -l ~/ | grep -E '^.[A-Z].[A-Z].e$'
```

**Exercise 10**.
```bash
ls ~/ | grep -E '^[a-zA-Z0-9]{4}$'
```

**Exercise 11**.
```bash
ls -1 /var/log | grep -E '\.log$'
```


